data.description: Beautifully updated half-duplex with modern amenities! Step inside to discover stylish vinyl flooring throughout, complemented by an updated kitchen featuring sleek stainless steel appliances. The newer roof, water heater and 2019 AC ensure peace of mind. Other recent updates include newer bathroom vanities and fixtures, interior doors, lighting and electrical receptacles, & 4 1/2'' floor trim adding a touch of upscale feel. Step outside to a spacious trussed screened patio, perfect for relaxing outside w/ a fully fenced backyard. This home is a must-see for those seeking comfort and style in an affordable location.
